Gwynne Shipman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gwynne_Shipman 0 Gwynne Shipman (born Beulah McDonald; November 8, 1909 – September 11, 2005) was an American film actress. She was married to the screenwriter Barry Shipman with whom she had a daughter Nina, who became an actress.
